<div class="jumbotron marqeta-main">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3">
      <h1 class="center">You just created a Card ...</h1>

      <div id="card">
        <p><%= image_tag 'marqeta-logo' %> <span id="title">MARQETA</span></p>
        <p><span id="number"><%= @card_number %></span></p>
        <p id="exp">Exp: <%= @exp %> <span id="CVV">CVV: <%= session[:card]['cvv_number'] %></span></p>
       
        <p id="name"><%= session[:user][:first_name] %>  </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="action-call center">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3">
      <h1>Now let's create a Transaction</h1>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-4">
      <%= form_for(@transaction) do |f| %>
        <%= f.text_field :amount, placeholder: "Enter an amount", required: true %>

        <%= f.submit "Create Transaction", class: "btn btn-primary" %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<br>
<br>

<div class="col-md-12  divider">
  <h3>SEE WHAT'S GOING ON BEHIND THE SCENES...</h3>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 info">
    <h4>CREATE A TRANSACTION</h4>
    <p>This will send a <span class="code">POST</span> request to <span class="code">/simulate/transaction</span>
    with the following body:</p>
    <pre><p class="code">{
    "amount": "**YOUR AMOUNT**",
    "mid": "123456890",
    "card_token": "**CARD TOKEN FROM PREVIOUS STEP**"
}</p></pre>
    <p>The code box above provides a JSON-formatted message body for creating a card. Note that this card will be active upon issue because of the card product's configuration.</p>
  </div>
</div>